<div class="row">
    <div class="col-lg-9 mx-auto">
        <div class="second-wrapper">
            <h2>Confindentiality</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="text-wrapper-third">
            <p>
                This page focuses on what information you would like to keep private and what
                information you would like to share with the public. For each data element below there are three options...
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-wrapper-fourth">
            <p>1) Public <span>(display this information on the advertisement for all to see)</span></p>
            <p>2) Protected <span>(display on advertisement but only show to business brokers, agents, abd advisors)</span></p>
            <p>3) Private <span>(do not display on the advertisement. this information is confidential)</span></p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-wrapper-fifth">
            <p>Biz-Hub recommends seller's consider carefully what information they wish to share with others. However, the more information you elect to share the greater your chances for are for being discovered.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

